description: This file defines data models related to portfolio holdings, including the 'Holding' class representing individual asset holdings with JSON serialization methods and the 'PortfolioSummary' class summarizing portfolio metrics.

classes.name: Holding
classes.description: Represents a financial asset holding with symbol, quantity, and average cost, including JSON serialization methods.

classes.name: PortfolioSummary
classes.description: Encapsulates a summary of a portfolio with total value, daily profit/loss, total profit/loss, and a list of holdings.

methods.name: Holding.fromJson
methods.description: Factory constructor to create a Holding instance from a JSON map.

methods.name: Holding.toJson
methods.description: Serializes a Holding instance to a JSON map.
